{"tid":1828643,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"|Switch|健身環大冒險 RingFit Advanture(6) 新年瘋狂減肥 ～ 遊戲語言跟你部機","createTime":"2020-01-18T04:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T07:21:22.000Z","uid":39478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"590c83461da3969eec9e7e3e32114b8c819bbb1e","tid":1828643,"uid":39478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:47:05.000Z","msg":"遊戲名稱：健身環大冒險<br />\n遊戲原名：RingFit Advanture<br />\n遊戲類型：體感冒險<br />\n對應平台：Nintendo Switch<br />\n發售日期：2019 年 10 月 18 日（台灣地區尚待確認）<br />\n建議售價：7980 日圓 + 稅<br />\n語言版本：繁體中文 / 簡體中文 / 英文 / 日文等<br />\n遊玩人數：1 人<br />\n年齡分級：普遍級<br />\n開發廠商：Nintendo<br />\n發行廠商：Nintendo<br />\n代理經銷：任天堂香港<br />\n官方網站：<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/ringadventure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Fringadventure%2F&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=540101aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/ringadventure/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLV2DjE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLV2DjE.jpg&h=831bba54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qzTGTS0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqzTGTS0.jpg&h=1c9699aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GaAFpZF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGaAFpZF.jpg&h=c953471b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XhN4REG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXhN4REG.jpg&h=5e41eff9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4bpREG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4bpREG.png&h=1cf1f416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n任天堂製作，即將於<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><em> 10 月 18 日</em></strong></span>推出的 Nintendo Switch 健身冒險遊戲套組《健身環大冒險（RingFit Advanture）》，「冒險讓你動起來（Adventures That Keep You Moving）」<br />\n<br />\n　《健身環大冒險》是針對 Nintendo Switch 推出的體感健身冒險遊戲，將活用 Joy-Con 動態感測的功能，搭配皮拉提斯拉力環設計的「Ring-Con」與繫在大腿上的「腿部固定帶」等專屬周邊，來感測使用者上下半身的動作。配合融入各式各樣健身動作的冒險遊戲，讓使用者透過娛樂性十足的電玩遊戲來達成健身的效果。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲提供超過40種健身項目，分別可鍛鍊手部、核心肌群、腿部肌肉，甚至可以模擬瑜伽、Pilates 等運動，以遊戲讓使用者達成健身的效果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sk69ijx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsk69ijx.jpg&h=19b30f63&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YDq2Djy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYDq2Djy.png&h=fea06a3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RM2o7cU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRM2o7cU.jpg&h=a04359da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\npost credit: 我係唔會驚 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請善用不推文回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160c0c81ac01d69c7123a853c9b949e1dc4b4abc","tid":1828643,"uid":39478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:49:58.000Z","msg":"原來已經有post請去此post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n|Switch|健身環大冒險 RingFit Advanture(6) 網購是個好朋友 Google常伴你左右<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1828322\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1828322</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"91ab6e11a6ce9dfc62bdb87489fe7eeaf44cf358","tid":1828643,"uid":114162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:47:58.000Z","msg":"想問下有無粵語語音<br />\n唔想聽普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60c8f8876d146156f7894cf6c250b00aadefd5c","tid":1828643,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:03:53.000Z","msg":"做要ring fit 覺得自己有quota成日走去飲可樂同珍珠奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後隻手係大隻左不過肚腩都大埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /